At x = R: B = \frac{\mu_0 I R^2}{2(R^2 + R^2)^{3/2}} = \frac{\mu_0 I R^2}{2(2R^2)^{3/2}} = \frac{\mu_0 I}{2R} \times \frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}}

Ratio: B_0 / B = 2\sqrt{2} : 1

