Circumference = L, so radius R = \frac{L}{2\pi}

Area = \pi R^2 = \pi \times \frac{L^2}{4\pi^2} = \frac{L^2}{4\pi}

Magnetic moment: M = IA = \frac{IL^2}{4\pi}

